om\": 782, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic history\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 815}, {\"ngram\": \"four medals\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"a single Games\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"a remarkable haul\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"only four events\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That perfect podium record will do well to survive the individual finals to come, not least because China - who, despite being run unexpectedly close by Mexico, made it four golds from four - will likely have two contenders in each.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999955309585675, \"rank\": 2.5341897627167366e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1129, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9964380765204052, \"rank\": 0.0035746129691744087, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That perfect podium record\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual finals\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"two contenders\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there are solo British hopes, too, that on this level of collective form must be taken extremely seriously, indeed.\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9957560712361502, \"rank\": 0.003241485291880996, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this level\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"collective form\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laugher and Harding were out of the pool almost as quickly as they were into it after nailing their sixth and final dive, embracing in celebration of the medal secured with a total score of 438.15.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Laugher\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"Harding\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"their sixth and final dive\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"celebration\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1489}, {\"ngram\": \"a total score\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The key moment though, had come in the previous round, when the pair stood at the edge of the board and sprung into the most difficult dive on their card.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1683, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The key moment\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"the previous round\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"the edge\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1615}, {\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1628}, {\"ngram\": \"the most difficult dive\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1668}, {\"ngram\": \"their card\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Typically, they had saved it until last, but after a butchered effort cost them a medal at the World Championships, a pre-Paris shakeup was forced.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1831, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a butchered effort\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1771}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1798}, {\"ngram\": \"a pre-Paris shakeup\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, ordinarily, it's a good dive but over the last year or so Anthony's had a struggle with it,\\\" Laugher, now a four-time Olympic medalist explained.\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1987, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good dive\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1870}, {\"ngram\": \"the last year\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"Anthony\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"a struggle\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"Laugher\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"a four-time Olympic medalist\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It felt like it was just too much pressure and we wanted to make that list order better.\\\"\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just too much pressure\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"that list order\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The routine -a forward two-and-a-half somersaults with three twists - has a 3.9 difficulty, higher even than anything the Chinese attempted here.\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2202, \"end\": 2209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.6437402146774928, \"rank\": 0.553236430312627, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The routine -a forward two-and-a-half somersaults\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"three twists\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"a 3.9 difficulty\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the hardest dive we do,\\\" Harding said.\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hardest dive\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"Harding\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In training, to get the adrenaline to do it is so difficult.\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2284}, {\"ngram\": \"the adrenaline\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's Jack's strongest dive so it's a no-brainer that it has to be there.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2341, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.9525925991996087, \"rank\": 0.02726040325804297, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a no-brainer\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, I am just so happy to get it in when it actually mattered.\\\"\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions Incredible days out and trips for autumn and winter In Doha, at the Worlds, it had scored them only 63 points,.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2609, \"end\": 2625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2736, \"end\": 2740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.756962895314094e-18, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"