"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair of Juan Celaya and Osmar Olvera delivered, though, as they had all morning, deservedly taking silver having made a contest out of what most arriving at the Aquatics Centre assumed would be a procession for the Chinese.\", \"from\": 3060, \"to\": 3287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3077, \"end\": 3083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celaya\", \"score\": 0.9999999999663487, \"rank\": 3.3516082438037646e-11, \"text\": \"Celaya\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celaya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celaya\"}, {\"begin\": 3088, \"end\": 3093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osmar_(footballer,_born_1988)\", \"score\": 0.6438963487818352, \"rank\": 0.35555555555554375, \"text\": \"Osmar\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osmar_(footballer,_born_1988)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osmar_(footballer,_born_1988)\"}, {\"begin\": 3094, \"end\": 3100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\", \"score\": 0.7837133084447123, \"rank\": 0.27597680073148556, \"text\": \"Olvera\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\"}, {\"begin\": 3279, \"end\": 3286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.6437402146774928, \"rank\": 0.553236430312627, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pair\", \"from\": 3060, \"to\": 3068}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3169}, {\"ngram\": \"a contest\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"the Aquatics Centre\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3240}, {\"ngram\": \"a procession\", \"from\": 3258, \"to\": 3270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heading into round five, Daoyi Long and Zongyuan Wang were in the unfamiliar position of leading the chasing pack after a strangely wobbly run.\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daoyi Long\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3324}, {\"ngram\": \"Zongyuan Wang\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3342}, {\"ngram\": \"the unfamiliar position\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3374}, {\"ngram\": \"the chasing pack\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3402}, {\"ngram\": \"a strangely wobbly run\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They delivered when it mattered most, but were not sure of victory until the very last dive of the day, as Mexico came up just two points short of the score needed to snatch gold.\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3540, \"end\": 3546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9964380765204052, \"rank\": 0.0035746129691744087, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 3492, \"to\": 3499}, {\"ngram\": \"the very last dive\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3524}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3535}, {\"ngram\": \"the score\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3589}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3607, \"to\": 3611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Harding, still breathless speaking in the mixed zone the best part of an hour later, talked mainly of relief at the culmination of a journey that began with in tears at his first ever session in Oldham, begging not to be sent off the end of the board.\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3809, \"end\": 3815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oldham_Athletic_A.F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999385588511553, \"rank\": 6.144378551098692e-05, \"text\": \"Oldham\", \"types\": [\"Q476028